{"tid":2337638,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英記者雲南查武肺 遭卡車攔路","createTime":"2020-12-23T12:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T12:14:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0c557921209c20702f28bd0164981591b3558fef","tid":2337638,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/ZHEMOJZIIFHNJLH7BY5NDWUWNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FZHEMOJZIIFHNJLH7BY5NDWUWNU%2F&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpyuJrf%2BHou%2F%2F5XtIYOa%2FW4Y%3D&h=e66c80f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201223%2FZHEMOJZIIFHNJLH7BY5NDWUWNU%2F&h=8c8b0cbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201223/ZHEMOJZIIFHNJLH7BY5NDWUWNU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英記者雲南查武肺 遭卡車攔路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EilbxJyQWhHHTzl0qbvW6HVnJDs=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DS7OYEH4ONFPXCOTWZAEFMJ42U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEilbxJyQWhHHTzl0qbvW6HVnJDs%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDS7OYEH4ONFPXCOTWZAEFMJ42U.jpg&h=7068a553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大貨車阻擋BBC採訪車輛的去路。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情爆發近一年，最先爆發的中國近來不斷撇清自己是源頭，卻不容許別人調查。英國廣播公司（BBC）記者沙磊（John Sudworth），近日到雲南採訪時遇上不少人為阻礙，除了被便衣公安監視，還有到任何重點地方採訪，都遇上大型卡車「故障」擋在路中央，無奈放棄採訪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e8KBRVSKuN8bkqKl5uJl5UQjptk=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MS5CBW5PIFGZLKQIBN3ITGGHKU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe8KBRVSKuN8bkqKl5uJl5UQjptk%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMS5CBW5PIFGZLKQIBN3ITGGHKU.jpg&h=3b6d95b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBBC記者沙磊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n便衣公安緊跟監視<br />\n<br />\n英國《星期日泰晤士報》早前報道指，雲南一處礦場2012年有六名工人染上不明肺炎，其中三人死亡。據報道，武漢病毒研究所的病毒學家石正麗曾對此礦場進行研究，發現一種名為RaTG13的冠狀病毒，與武漢肺炎新型冠狀病毒相似度高達96.2%。BBC記者沙磊近日前往調查，但一路上並不順利。<br />\n<br />\n沙磊昨在BBC的報道中表示，「便衣公安和其他官員搭着未標示任何字樣的車輛跟在我們後面。當我們因為道路狀況必須迴轉時，也緊跟着我們」、「我們沿路都遇上路障，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n沙磊也曾電郵詢問石正麗對世衞即將派員赴華調查的看法，石回覆指：「只要。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司"},{"pid":"bc35462f23bf24d0bdd3dc47caec72caa81ef38c","tid":2337638,"uid":43557,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T12:14:17.000Z","msg":"佢係咪去錯地方？應該去美國先岩wo"}]}